<encodingDesc n="1.5">
<projectDesc><p>This transcription was made by the Verbum Project as part of an online and printed edition of the Old Latin versions of John between 2003 and 2010.</p></projectDesc>
<editorialDecl><p>This transcription covers the whole fragment. The text contained is John 19:27-20:11. It was based on White's edition, which doesn't always identify the correctors, although it does mark a correction later on as s.m.. The transcription includes foliation, lineation, all punctuation and abbreviations. The initial transcription file was a plain text file for use with COLLATE. Further information about the procedures followed may be found in the electronic edition at <ptr target="http://www.iohannes.com/vetuslatina/"/></p>
<p>This second edition of the file was converted to XML by Catherine Smith using the project's Python conversion scripts 1.0.</p>
<p>The XML specifications used are version 1.5 of the IGNTP Guidelines available at <ptr target="http://epapers.bham.ac.uk/1892/"/></p></editorialDecl></encodingDesc>

